</div>
<div data-type="commentary" id="fs-id1170571035302" data-element-type="hint"><div data-type="title">Hint</div>
<p id="fs-id1170571545540">Use <a href="#fs-id1170571654206" class="autogenerated-content">[link]</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p id="fs-id1170572642379">In the next example we put our knowledge of various types of limits to use to analyze the behavior of a function at several different points.</p>
<div data-type="example" id="fs-id1170572642384">
