<div data-type="exercise" id="fs-id1170572403244">
<div data-type="problem" id="fs-id1170572403246">
<p id="fs-id1170572403249">To which mathematical constant does the limit in the preceding exercise appear to be getting closer?</p>
</div>
</div>
<p id="fs-id1170572403269">In the following exercises, use the given values to set up a table to evaluate the limits. Round your solutions to eight decimal places.</p>
<div data-type="exercise" id="fs-id1170572403273">
